{
  "text": "In a companion paper [CITATION_1] , we describe two speech tests that can be used with children aged from 2 to 9 years so as to obtain meaningful results and to avoid floor and ceiling effects. These tests, together with some others, were used in the present study to compare the effectiveness of DSL i/o, DSL V, and NAL-NL1 for children from 2 to 9 years of age.",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "205478784"
